<div id="review_2431607459" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2431607459" />
    <a title="Heather" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/2756536-heather"><img alt="Heather" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1508096337p2/2756536.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2431607459?book_show_action=true">Sep 21, 2018</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Heather" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Heather" href="/user/show/2756536-heather">Heather</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9780312374631" href="/book/show/1093493.And_the_Band_Played_On">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2431607459" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer4656990121591341056">This book took me a long time to read. I could only read small bits at a time. It was both informative and heartbreaking. And it made me think of friends I&apos;ve lost. But other friends of mine actually lived through this time. It was a complete travesty how long it took this country to come to action against AIDS. </span>
  <span id="freeText4656990121591341056" style="display:none">This book took me a long time to read. I could only read small bits at a time. It was both informative and heartbreaking. And it made me think of friends I've lost. But other friends of mine actually lived through this time. It was a complete travesty how long it took this country to come to action against AIDS. </span>
  <a data-text-id="4656990121591341056" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


