<span id="freeTextContainer17856474831620822792">Tremendously thorough, very engaging, heartbreaking and furious. This was, sadly, a perfect book to read given the recent administration&apos;s demonstrated negligence and ineffectiveness in dealing with large-scale crises. Especially crises that are most devastating to vulnerable communities (i.e., everyone not white, cis, straight, Christian, male). </span>
  <span id="freeText17856474831620822792" style="display:none">Tremendously thorough, very engaging, heartbreaking and furious. This was, sadly, a perfect book to read given the recent administration's demonstrated negligence and ineffectiveness in dealing with large-scale crises. Especially crises that are most devastating to vulnerable communities (i.e., everyone not white, cis, straight, Christian, male). </span>
