      <div id="aboutAuthor" class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/author/show/15877.Randy_Shilts">About Randy Shilts</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
          <div class='bookAuthorProfile'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__topContainer'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__photoContainer'>
<a href="/author/show/15877.Randy_Shilts"><div class='bookAuthorProfile__photo' style='background-image: url(https://images.gr-assets.com/authors/1221789810p3/15877.jpg);'></div>
</a></div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__widgetContainer'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__name'>
<a href="/author/show/15877.Randy_Shilts">Randy Shilts
</a></div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__followerCount'>
142
followers
</div>

</div>
</div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer16000395703277604731">Randy Shilts was a highly acclaimed, pioneering gay American journalist and author. He worked as a reporter for both <i>The Advocate</i> and the <i>San Francisco Chronicle</i>, as well as for San Francisco Bay Area television stations.</span>

</div>
</div>

